description: Provides the details for the GuardDuty administrator account associated with the current GuardDuty member account.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the detector of the GuardDuty member account. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The ID of the account used as the administrator account.

nested_items.name: InvitationId
nested_items.description: The value used to validate the administrator account to the member account.

nested_items.name: RelationshipStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the relationship between the administrator and member accounts.

nested_items.name: InvitedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the invitation was sent.
